summary: Brie Larson playing a lesbian? Yes -- yes she has.
title: Brie Larson playing a lesbian? Yes -- yes she has.
body:
Her character in the 2012 music video of JJAMZ - Never Enough seemingly shows a “low key lesbian” in an unrequited love situation with her friend. Despite the writers of the song explaining it’s more of a friendship/sisterhood relationship it’s undeniable the video shown more of a pure heartbreak of love (heck they even had the Life is Strange scene-esque where Max and Chloe dipped in the pool together) Also the lyrics of the song shares a deep connection between two people who has shared a bond stronger than most people.

Enjoy the gifs, the video, beautiful song, the whole thing that I’m sure a lot of you can relate to.

https://oneweekoneband.tumblr.com/post/98891615074/never-enough-jjamz-never-enough-is-a-song
